Drink this tonic to recover.

00:02:28.463 --> 00:02:29.503
Liluo,

00:02:31.222 --> 00:02:36.702
is the sanctuary going to give you
the Wujing Saintess' battle robe

00:02:37.303 --> 00:02:39.262
to welcome you to the sanctuary?

00:02:40.422 --> 00:02:42.022
You're finally going to be free.

00:02:42.023 --> 00:02:43.542
I've had enough.

