Feng Zhilou ruined everything today.

00:02:46.262 --> 00:02:48.422
So what if I'm the Wujing Saintess now?

00:02:48.502 --> 00:02:50.302
Prince Shang called off our engagement

00:02:50.303 --> 00:02:52.063
for the sake of that wretch.

00:02:53.063 --> 00:02:54.383
How could that be?

00:02:54.422 --> 00:02:55.462
What good is playing

00:02:55.463 --> 00:02:57.223
the dutiful daughter with you every day?

00:02:58.583 --> 00:02:59.663
Liluo,

00:03:00.382 --> 00:03:03.022
I know you resent me.

00:03:03.422 --> 00:03:05.822
But I'm your mother.

00:03:06.143 --> 00:03:08.701
I've given you everything I could.

00:03:08.702 --> 00:03:10.262
Shut up.

00:03:10.903 --> 00:03:13.183
I'm not your daughter.

00:03:13.903 --> 00:03:16.343
I'm the princess of Wujing City.

00:03:16.903 --> 00:03:17.862
Liluo,

00:03:18.463 --> 00:03:20.223
why do you speak such nonsense?

00:03:20.262 --> 00:03:22.302
Why would you say such things?

00:03:27.143 --> 00:03:28.702
What are you standing there for?

00:04:05.863 --> 00:04:06.663
Mother.

00:04:07.903 --> 00:04:08.623
Mother.

00:04:09.422 --> 00:04:11.103
I've come to rescue you, Mother.

00:04:13.942 --> 00:04:15.262
My good daughter.

00:04:16.143 --> 00:04:17.343
Don't worry.

00:04:18.542 --> 00:04:19.982
I'm fine.

00:04:22.143 --> 00:04:23.583
Don't be sad.

00:04:24.622 --> 00:04:27.583
It's okay even if
you don't marry a Dragon.

00:04:28.583 --> 00:04:30.542
As long as you're free,

00:04:31.102 --> 00:04:33.382
you can do whatever you want.

00:04:35.182 --> 00:04:36.223
Mother,

00:04:37.343 --> 00:04:38.862
I'm Feng Zhilou.

00:04:38.943 --> 00:04:40.263
I'm not Liluo.

00:04:40.503 --> 00:04:42.062
I'm your daughter.

00:04:42.222 --> 00:04:43.462
I'm Feng Zhilou.

00:04:43.463 --> 00:04:44.783
Feng Zhilou?

00:04:48.503 --> 00:04:49.343
Mother.

00:04:49.862 --> 00:04:50.621
You're the one

00:04:50.622 --> 00:04:52.903
who seduced Prince Shang?

00:04:55.263 --> 00:04:56.263
No.

00:04:56.622 --> 00:04:57.463
Mother,

00:04:58.383 --> 00:04:59.542
I'm Feng Zhilou.

00:04:59.943 --> 00:05:01.582
I'm your real daughter.

00:05:01.583 --> 00:05:02.741
Liluo is not your daughter.

00:05:02.742 --> 00:05:03.502
Do you remember me?

00:05:03.503 --> 00:05:04.142
I'm Feng Zhilou,

00:05:04.143 --> 00:05:05.062
Mother.

00:05:05.102 --> 00:05:06.463
Stop talking.

00:05:07.023 --> 00:05:09.062
You're the reason Liluo was rejected.

00:05:09.263 --> 00:05:11.103
The reason she won't forgive me.

00:05:11.503 --> 00:05:13.422
Why have you come to me now?

00:05:13.463 --> 00:05:14.422
Where is Liluo?

00:05:14.583 --> 00:05:16.263
What have you done to her?

00:05:16.503 --> 00:05:17.301
Mother,

00:05:17.302 --> 00:05:18.622
listen to me.

00:05:20.062 --> 00:05:21.942
I came from Feng Manor.

00:05:22.143 --> 00:05:24.103
My father's name is Feng Qingfeng.

00:05:24.943 --> 00:05:27.263
I've had no spiritual root
since I was young.

00:05:28.143 --> 00:05:29.661
My father told me

00:05:29.662 --> 00:05:32.263
you left Feng Manor 18 years ago.

00:05:32.343 --> 00:05:33.582
After you came to Wujing City,

00:05:33.583 --> 00:05:35.263
there was no news of you.

00:05:35.383 --> 00:05:37.142
But I have your portrait.

00:05:37.143 --> 00:05:38.823
You left us a portrait.

00:05:39.222 --> 00:05:40.542
A portrait?

00:05:44.143 --> 00:05:46.103
How could you have my portrait?

00:05:46.143 --> 00:05:47.143
No way.

00:05:47.542 --> 00:05:48.782
I don't believe it.

00:05:48.783 --> 00:05:49.982
You're lying to me.

00:05:50.943 --> 00:05:51.741
Leave.

00:05:51.742 --> 00:05:52.582
I don't believe you.

00:05:52.583 --> 00:05:53.621
Leave.

00:05:53.622 --> 00:05:54.541
Go away.

00:05:54.542 --> 00:05:56.181
I really am your daughter,

00:05:56.182 --> 00:05:57.103
Mother.

00:05:59.903 --> 00:06:00.942
Someone, help.

00:06:01.703 --> 00:06:02.982
Someone, help!

00:06:04.463 --> 00:06:05.221
Li Yue.

00:06:05.222 --> 00:06:05.621
Mother.

00:06:05.622 --> 00:06:07.062
I want to see Li Yue!

00:06:07.783 --> 00:06:08.541
Someone, help!

00:06:08.542 --> 00:06:09.741
Mother, listen to me.

00:06:09.742 --> 00:06:10.621
I want to see Li Yue!

00:06:10.622 --> 00:06:11.942
They're all deceiving you, Mother.

00:06:11.943 --> 00:06:13.862
She promised me

00:06:14.062 --> 00:06:16.022
that she would bring my daughter here...

00:06:16.023 --> 00:06:16.541
Mother.

00:06:16.542 --> 00:06:18.663
and raise her like a princess.

00:06:18.783 --> 00:06:21.182
I've always
stayed in Feng Manor, Mother.

00:06:22.062 --> 00:06:23.221
She wouldn't dare lie to me.

00:06:23.222 --> 00:06:23.861
Mother.

00:06:23.862 --> 00:06:25.502
She swore to heaven.

00:06:25.503 --> 00:06:25.942
Mother.

00:06:25.943 --> 00:06:27.101
I don't believe it.

00:06:27.102 --> 00:06:28.541
How could this be possible?

00:06:28.542 --> 00:06:29.902
How could this be possible?

00:06:29.903 --> 00:06:32.343
You're lying to me. You must be lying.

00:06:34.222 --> 00:06:35.301
No.

00:06:35.302 --> 00:06:36.062
No.

00:06:36.263 --> 00:06:37.782
Something's wrong.

00:06:37.783 --> 00:06:39.902
Everything's wrong. Someone, help.

00:06:39.903 --> 00:06:41.262
Li Yue.

00:06:41.263 --> 00:06:42.621
Li Yue!

00:06:42.622 --> 00:06:44.622
Mother.

00:06:44.862 --> 00:06:46.542
Li Yue!

00:07:06.422 --> 00:07:08.143
I've found my mother.

00:07:09.982 --> 00:07:11.783
Li Yue and Liluo locked her

00:07:12.463 --> 00:07:13.942
in the dungeon,

00:07:15.742 --> 00:07:17.223
kept her in total darkness,

00:07:19.903 --> 00:07:22.982
and tortured her
until she's barely human.

00:07:25.662 --> 00:07:28.463
How can I possibly save her?

00:07:31.783 --> 00:07:33.663
When I went to see her,

00:07:36.583 --> 00:07:39.062
I was so close to her.

00:07:40.463 --> 00:07:42.742
I'm her real daughter.

00:07:45.343 --> 00:07:47.742
But she just doesn't recognize me.

00:07:49.503 --> 00:07:50.663
Zhilou,

00:07:51.982 --> 00:07:53.221
I've explained Li Yue's

00:07:53.222 --> 00:07:54.823
false identity to the sanctuary.

00:07:56.422 --> 00:07:57.981
But she has been in Wujing City

00:07:57.982 --> 00:07:59.742
for 18 years as the city lord.

00:08:00.583 --> 00:08:02.942
Liluo's saintess bloodline
has also been verified.

00:08:03.463 --> 00:08:05.542
The sanctuary doesn't believe my words.

00:08:08.463 --> 00:08:10.622
So no one cares

00:08:11.422 --> 00:08:13.263
what the true Wujing Saintess

00:08:14.062 --> 00:08:15.622
looks like.

00:08:16.263 --> 00:08:17.783
Just as long as someone

00:08:18.583 --> 00:08:19.622
plays the role.

00:08:22.222 --> 00:08:23.062
Plays the role?

00:08:25.583 --> 00:08:26.663
You're right.

00:08:27.143 --> 00:08:28.502
Since it's all a performance,

00:08:29.182 --> 00:08:31.103
we might as well play along with them.

00:08:37.182 --> 00:08:38.343
Greetings, Young Lord.

00:08:41.942 --> 00:08:43.061
Is the one locked in here

00:08:43.062 --> 00:08:45.223
my mother and sister's blood vessel?

00:08:47.422 --> 00:08:48.223
Never mind.

00:08:48.503 --> 00:08:50.063
I'm taking her away today.

00:08:50.223 --> 00:08:51.463
Step aside.

00:08:51.743 --> 00:08:52.862
Young Lord,

00:08:53.103 --> 00:08:54.181
if you take her away,

00:08:54.182 --> 00:08:56.063
you're taking my life.

00:08:56.302 --> 00:08:57.943
Am I the one taking your life,

00:08:58.182 --> 00:08:59.902
or is it Princess Liluo?

00:09:00.342 --> 00:09:02.102
I didn't know that Wujing City

00:09:02.103 --> 00:09:03.943
is ruled by Princess Liluo alone.

00:09:09.182 --> 00:09:11.103
Have the apothecary collect his body.

00:09:11.223 --> 00:09:12.622
Don't let him be an eyesore here.

00:09:13.503 --> 00:09:15.223
You may inform your master

00:09:15.302 --> 00:09:16.622
that I've slain a guard.

00:09:16.903 --> 00:09:17.782
Yes, Young Lord.

00:09:33.863 --> 00:09:35.183
What do you want now?

00:09:35.702 --> 00:09:37.742
I've given you all I could.

00:09:38.023 --> 00:09:39.183
My eyes,

00:09:39.422 --> 00:09:40.543
my freedom,

00:09:40.582 --> 00:09:41.742
my flesh and blood,

00:09:41.942 --> 00:09:43.142
all to you.

00:09:43.223 --> 00:09:45.022
Can you return my daughter to me?

00:09:46.822 --> 00:09:47.823
Miss Yue,

00:09:48.182 --> 00:09:49.303
I'm Li Yan.

00:09:49.662 --> 00:09:51.862
You once showed me this world.

00:09:52.743 --> 00:09:53.583
I'm sorry.

00:09:54.062 --> 00:09:55.262
I never knew

00:09:55.263 --> 00:09:56.982
my world came at a price like this.

00:10:09.023 --> 00:10:10.103
Yan,

00:10:10.582 --> 00:10:12.982
soon, you will see the light again.

00:10:13.023 --> 00:10:14.862
As long as you and Liluo are with me,

00:10:14.863 --> 00:10:16.742
I don't mind being blind.

00:10:17.582 --> 00:10:18.583
Come with me.

00:10:25.903 --> 00:10:27.782
This is the one who will heal your eyes.

00:10:27.783 --> 00:10:28.742
Really?

00:10:28.743 --> 00:10:30.701
I will be able
to see everything they say?

00:10:30.702 --> 00:10:32.142
Thank you so much.

00:10:34.023 --> 00:10:34.982
Child,

00:10:35.383 --> 00:10:36.823
if you can see,

00:10:37.023 --> 00:10:38.103
promise me

00:10:38.383 --> 00:10:40.502
you will treat all you see
with kindness.

00:10:40.582 --> 00:10:41.902
What is your name?

00:10:42.182 --> 00:10:43.862
You can call me Miss Yue.

00:10:44.503 --> 00:10:46.142
Miss Yue.

00:10:46.623 --> 00:10:47.902
I promise you,

00:10:47.942 --> 00:10:50.463
once I can see, I will come visit you.

00:10:53.623 --> 00:10:54.543
This is...

00:10:54.903 --> 00:10:56.622
This is my eye.

00:10:56.623 --> 00:10:58.823
My eyes were given to a boy.

00:10:59.383 --> 00:11:00.703
He promised me

00:11:01.422 --> 00:11:03.943
he would
treat everything he sees kindly.

00:11:04.623 --> 00:11:05.862
I've been trying my best.

00:11:06.903 --> 00:11:08.463
Miss Yue, please believe me.

00:11:08.702 --> 00:11:10.022
Li Yue is my mother.

00:11:10.023 --> 00:11:11.502
Liluo is my younger sister.

00:11:11.623 --> 00:11:12.943
They deceived you.

00:11:13.263 --> 00:11:15.022
Feng Zhilou is your daughter.

00:11:15.302 --> 00:11:16.823
You mean to say

00:11:17.182 --> 00:11:19.502
Liluo is not my real daughter?

00:11:19.623 --> 00:11:20.581
My real daughter

00:11:20.582 --> 00:11:22.703
is Feng Zhilou from Feng Manor?

00:11:26.143 --> 00:11:27.022
Mother.

00:11:29.903 --> 00:11:31.382
I'm Feng Zhilou.

00:11:33.542 --> 00:11:35.622
I truly am your daughter.

00:11:39.783 --> 00:11:40.982
Zhilou.

00:11:46.103 --> 00:11:48.742
Are you really my daughter?

00:11:48.983 --> 00:11:50.142
Zhilou.

00:11:53.103 --> 00:11:55.823
How have you been all these years?

00:11:58.462 --> 00:12:00.622
I am sorry.

00:12:14.422 --> 00:12:16.262
We should leave now.

00:12:19.342 --> 00:12:20.022
Are you sure?

00:12:20.023 --> 00:12:20.821
Sure.

00:12:20.822 --> 00:12:22.742
The Young Lord killed the guard

00:12:22.743 --> 00:12:24.382
to bring Feng Zhilou into the dungeon.

00:12:24.743 --> 00:12:27.301
That dungeon will be
Feng Zhilou's final resting place.

00:12:27.302 --> 00:12:28.463
Stop right there.

00:12:28.702 --> 00:12:29.862
What's this?

00:12:41.103 --> 00:12:42.821
So this is Li Yan's

00:12:42.822 --> 00:12:45.262
lousy scare tactic to warn others?

00:12:45.983 --> 00:12:47.423
What a bother!

00:12:48.422 --> 00:12:50.502
No discernment at all.

00:12:50.983 --> 00:12:53.502
Must you show me this dead body?

00:12:53.942 --> 00:12:56.061
You're always bowing your head.

00:12:56.062 --> 00:12:58.821
No wonder the apothecary
assigned such tasks to you.

00:12:58.822 --> 00:12:59.622
Get lost!

00:13:18.702 --> 00:13:20.103
Feng Zhilou,

00:13:20.462 --> 00:13:23.022
you can't run this time.

00:13:23.903 --> 00:13:24.862
Sir,

00:13:25.023 --> 00:13:26.902
I came here with the Young Lord

00:13:27.223 --> 00:13:29.022
without any intention of running away.

00:13:29.103 --> 00:13:30.142
Remember,

00:13:30.143 --> 00:13:32.223
this is Wujing City.

00:13:32.623 --> 00:13:34.541
So what if you have nine spiritual roots

00:13:34.542 --> 00:13:36.262
and are a martial expert?

00:13:36.263 --> 00:13:37.823
If you dare resist,

00:13:38.342 --> 00:13:40.703
your family will suffer.

00:13:41.103 --> 00:13:42.982
I know my place.

00:13:43.342 --> 00:13:44.941
The nobles of Wujing City
can ruin people

00:13:44.942 --> 00:13:46.463
with a single word.

00:13:46.582 --> 00:13:47.382
What chance

00:13:47.383 --> 00:13:48.982
do I, a nobody, have?

00:13:49.223 --> 00:13:51.022
Good thing you know that.

00:13:51.342 --> 00:13:53.661
Even if you take Yue away,

00:13:53.662 --> 00:13:56.142
you can't escape Wujing City
with a loser

00:13:56.143 --> 00:13:57.782
with no martial cultivation.

00:14:00.103 --> 00:14:01.142
Where is she?

00:14:05.143 --> 00:14:06.223
Where is she?

00:14:37.903 --> 00:14:39.421
Feng Zhilou,

00:14:39.422 --> 00:14:41.222
how dare you help a prisoner escape?

00:14:41.223 --> 00:14:42.022
Guards!

00:14:42.582 --> 00:14:43.862
Seize her now!

00:14:43.863 --> 00:14:44.782
Wait.

00:14:46.662 --> 00:14:48.823
Who allowed you to arrest her
in my presence?

00:14:50.462 --> 00:14:51.782
Liluo, tell me.

00:14:52.062 --> 00:14:53.982
Who did Miss Zhilou help escape

00:14:54.023 --> 00:14:56.262
that you need to make such a commotion?

00:14:57.103 --> 00:14:58.103
Li Yan,

00:14:58.223 --> 00:14:59.782
you traitorous wretch.

00:14:59.783 --> 00:15:01.382
Don't play dumb with me.

00:15:05.942 --> 00:15:07.823
Even if you're the Wujing Saintess,

00:15:08.062 --> 00:15:09.742
I'm the Young Lord of Wujing City

00:15:09.743 --> 00:15:11.063
and your brother.

00:15:11.503 --> 00:15:13.461
Who allowed you to act out here?

00:15:13.462 --> 00:15:13.982
You...

00:15:13.983 --> 00:15:14.902
Besides,

00:15:15.383 --> 00:15:17.343
you might not even marry a Dragon.

00:15:17.623 --> 00:15:19.502
Did you just slap me?

00:15:19.903 --> 00:15:21.823
If you were not my sister,

00:15:22.023 --> 00:15:23.742
I would have done the same long ago.

00:15:25.743 --> 00:15:27.063
And you lot,

00:15:27.783 --> 00:15:29.463
who are you pointing your blades at?

00:15:32.182 --> 00:15:34.183
We have no intention to offend you.

00:15:34.623 --> 00:15:37.382
We only came to arrest Feng Zhilou.

00:15:39.942 --> 00:15:41.181
May I ask, sir,

00:15:41.182 --> 00:15:42.382
what is the reason?

00:15:43.302 --> 00:15:44.821
Miss Zhilou,

00:15:44.822 --> 00:15:46.941
what are you doing in this dungeon?

00:15:46.942 --> 00:15:49.463
This place holds
the most dangerous criminals.

00:15:49.702 --> 00:15:50.982
Do you intend

00:15:51.743 --> 00:15:53.343
to break someone out?

00:15:55.263 --> 00:15:56.543
I'm standing right here.

00:15:57.223 --> 00:15:58.583
Have I broken anyone out?

00:15:59.023 --> 00:16:00.063
Sir,

00:16:00.942 --> 00:16:02.423
I'm here to see someone.

00:16:02.942 --> 00:16:04.782
That's quite a surprise.

00:16:05.103 --> 00:16:07.142
Who could be important enough for you

00:16:07.143 --> 00:16:09.301
to beg our Young Lord
to come and see them?

00:16:09.302 --> 00:16:11.543
Am I not important enough for that?

00:16:24.062 --> 00:16:25.701
Your Highness,

00:16:25.702 --> 00:16:27.502
what brings you to the dungeon?

00:16:29.143 --> 00:16:30.862
When have we Dragons

00:16:31.342 --> 00:16:33.463
ever needed to report to you?

00:16:46.903 --> 00:16:48.461
I'm the true Wujing Saintess.

00:16:48.462 --> 00:16:50.103
I'm the future Dragon Queen.

00:16:50.542 --> 00:16:51.862
Chu Moshang,

00:16:51.942 --> 00:16:54.022
how can you do this to me
again and again?

00:16:54.983 --> 00:16:56.022
Dragon Queen?

00:16:56.582 --> 00:16:57.622
Only in your dreams.

00:16:59.542 --> 00:17:00.561
Now, move.

00:17:00.562 --> 00:17:04.949
♪Memories rise and fall,
lost in a fleeting haze♪

00:17:04.950 --> 00:17:10.157
♪In a dream, I see him
who has gone far away♪

00:17:11.825 --> 00:17:17.249
♪Pondered each word to ask how you fare♪

00:17:17.250 --> 00:17:22.341
♪Twelve years gone,
only longing left to bear♪

00:17:22.342 --> 00:17:23.983
Hide here for now.

00:17:24.102 --> 00:17:25.262
We'll find your mother

00:17:25.263 --> 00:17:26.462
once things calm down.

00:17:26.550 --> 00:17:29.782
♪Oaths once strong like mountains,
now fading away♪

00:17:30.342 --> 00:17:30.974
Understood,

00:17:31.743 --> 00:17:33.222
my Dragon God.

00:17:33.423 --> 00:17:34.581
Thank you for your plan.

00:17:34.582 --> 00:17:36.702
You rescued my mother
without anyone knowing.

00:17:36.703 --> 00:17:38.911
♪My world reversed,
and everything fell silent♪

00:17:38.912 --> 00:17:40.782
♪A sudden breeze
shakes blossoms from the tree♪

00:17:40.783 --> 00:17:42.063
But she needs to hide

00:17:42.142 --> 00:17:43.624
at the apothecary for now.

00:17:45.223 --> 00:17:47.023
With Hunbao and Xiaoyu
taking care of her,

00:17:47.542 --> 00:17:48.461
I feel at ease.

00:17:48.462 --> 00:17:51.124
♪When all turns fickle,
who can tell truth from the dream?♪

00:17:51.125 --> 00:17:54.132
♪Longing will be etched
between my brows♪

00:18:02.262 --> 00:18:08.036
♪Like petals fall, gone with the clouds♪

00:18:08.037 --> 00:18:14.032
♪Like stars fade fast in open skies♪

00:18:14.149 --> 00:18:19.848
♪Like snowflakes melting softly
in the evening haze♪

00:18:19.849 --> 00:18:26.173
♪Like your fleeting glance
that gave me one brief dream's grace♪

00:18:26.174 --> 00:18:32.107
♪Like fireflies flicker
through wild grass, fleeting light♪

00:18:32.274 --> 00:18:37.844
♪Like evening breeze
that stirs soft hair in twilight♪

00:18:38.124 --> 00:18:43.848
♪Like fleeting thoughts
that surge and then unwind♪

00:18:43.849 --> 00:18:49.786
♪Chance meetings fade,
just empty rooms left behind♪

00:18:49.787 --> 00:18:55.419
♪You brought a wave
that stirred a wild, restless sea♪

00:18:55.699 --> 00:19:01.594
♪Light as a feather,
yet it sank an island deep in me♪

00:19:01.774 --> 00:19:08.332
♪In that one moment,
life's grip I couldn't break or sway♪

00:19:08.337 --> 00:19:14.094
♪Leaving me lost in memories,
small and fading away♪